OL,3,CBritish Library workers to strike in
OL,4,Cpay dispute
OL,6,FWorkers at the British Library are to
OL,7,Fstrike in a dispute over pay.
OL,9,FThe Public and Commercial Services
OL,10,Funion (PCS) said more than 300 of its
OL,11,Fmembers at the site in London will
OL,12,Fwalk out from October 27 to November 9
OL,13,Fafter voting by 98% in favour of
OL,14,Findustrial action.
OL,16,FThe union said the workers faced a
OL,17,Fsecond consecutive year of a below-
OL,18,Finflation pay rise.
