OL,3,CBritish Library workers to strike in
OL,4,Cpay dispute
OL,6,FPCS general secretary Fran Heathcote
OL,7,Fsaid: "A near unanimous vote for
OL,8,Fstrike action is just a small glimpse
OL,9,Finto the strength of feeling among our
OL,10,Fmembers at the British Library.
OL,12,F"They are livid at yet another
OL,13,Finsulting pay offer that does little
OL,14,Fto alleviate the health problems that
OL,15,Fmany suffer from because of low pay.
OL,17,F"Nor does it come close to ending the
OL,18,Fneed for many to work second jobs and
OL,19,Ftake out loans to pay their bills and
OL,20,Fmeet their housing costs.
