OL,3,CBritish Library workers to strike in
OL,4,Cpay dispute
OL,6,F"The employer's well-paid executives
OL,7,Fneed to take the blinkers off and
OL,8,Funderstand that our hard-working
OL,9,Fmembers are what makes the British
OL,10,FLibrary the vital cultural institution
OL,11,Fthat it is."
OL,13,FA British Library spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"Following conversations with trade
OL,15,Funions, the British Library has made a
OL,16,Fformal pay offer of 3% for the year
OL,17,F2025/26, which is weighted to enhance
OL,18,Fbenefits for our lower pay bands ` all
OL,19,Fstaff would receive a minimum of a
OL,20,Fconsolidated increase of 2.4% or #800
OL,21,F(whichever is the higher).
