OL,3,CBritish Library workers to strike in
OL,4,Cpay dispute
OL,6,F"The Library has also reaffirmed its
OL,7,Fcommitment to being a living wage
OL,8,Ffoundation employer, under which our
OL,9,Flower-paid employees are likely to
OL,10,Freceive a substantially higher
OL,11,Fpercentage increase.
OL,13,F"Separately, a restructure of senior
OL,14,Fmanagement is under way, however,
OL,15,Fdetails of this process remain
OL,16,Fconfidential while those who are
OL,17,Faffected are consulted.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
